      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "The former **time-since-reconcile**, **reconcile-duration**, and **active gRPC streams** panels are **restored above** (their `edge_cp_*` emitters landed in `internal/xds/metrics.go`), and the new **Proxies behind published config** panels export the delivery-divergence signal.\n\nStill without an emitter (see FOLLOW-UP in `observability/prometheus/alerts/control-plane.yaml`):\n- **DB pool idle/waiting** (`edge_cp_db_pool_idle`/`_waiting`) \u2014 the control-plane store's pgxpool exposes `Stat()`, but the store hides it behind its interfaces; emitting it needs an `internal/store` change.\n- **Snapshot-version-by-node** (`edge_cp_snapshot_version`) \u2014 obsolete since versions became content hashes (#47); the *Proxies behind published config* panels are its successor.\n\nRestore each in the same change that adds its emitter."
      }
